notes_display: In Historical Sketches of the Paper Currency of the American Colonies by Henry Phillips, Jr. (1865). Given to Dr. Jesse C. Green in 1890. Leaf 56P.
issue_place_s: Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, United States of America
issue_obverse_legend_s: TEN SHILLINGS. THIS BILL shall pass current for TEN SHILLINGS within the Province of Pennsilvania, according to an Act of Assembly, made in the 33d Year of the Reign of King GEORGE II. Dated May 1, 1760. TEN SHILL.
issue_reverse_legend_s: TEN SHILLINGS. | To Counterfeit is DEATH | Printed by B. FRANKLIN, and D. HALL. 1760.
